{"tid":1805064,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"革命舞序 好高汁","createTime":"2019-12-31T11:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T11:41:50.000Z","uid":266343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d966f16fc4ad8889bc15029322759755b911143f","tid":1805064,"uid":266343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"【特別分享】橫跨十八屆科大「老鬼」以舞明志　盼予港人未來一個盼望<br />\n<br />\n十二月某個寒夜，數十名身穿黑衣、黃巾蒙面的舞者凌晨4、5點開始爬上獅子山，抬著大量攝影器材和「香港民主女神像」，趕在日出時份在山頂跳一段舞，送給香港人。這支舞名為《革命舞序》，由橫跨十八屆的科大畢業生擔任舞者、製作影片，他們盼以音樂與舞蹈記錄反送中運動的點滴，凝聚每一位為堅守香港未來而無私付出的人。 「我哋希望透過呢隻舞，比個盼望全香港人，令佢哋知道呢半年有好多事情發生，但唔會打低我哋，反而會令香港人更堅定、頑強，我哋係唔會驚㗎！」《革命舞序》發起人之一 Harry（化名）說道&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n訪問全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37x5Znl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37x5Znl&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=e7ed9a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37x5Znl</a><br />\n<br />\n革命舞序 Danzmocrazy<br />\n#DANZMOCRAZY #DANCE4HK #革命舞序<br />\n<br />\n多謝一班熱愛舞蹈嘅科大畢業生<br />\n<br />\n#2020繼續抗爭<br />\n#hkerstandwithhk<br />\n#革命無罪<br />\n<br />\nig : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B6tkJfVHuJJ/?igshid=1shu0bm35r5xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB6tkJfVHuJJ%2F%3Figshid%3D1shu0bm35r5xc&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=4755c84f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B6tkJfVHuJJ/?igshid=1shu0bm35r5xc</a><br />\n<br />\nfb: <a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1YMGWI33lOVn3Lmz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1YMGWI33lOVn3Lmz&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=51579fbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1YMGWI33lOVn3Lmz</a><br />\n<br />\nyoutube: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/zGadfiEIPIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzGadfiEIPIg&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=a7adead6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zGadfiEIPIg</a>"}]}